OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud will
OL,6,Fbreak up for most overnight, with
OL,7,Fclearing skies and easing winds, but
OL,8,Fremaining gusty along the coast. Cloud
OL,9,Fmay linger across western hills.
OL,10,FRelatively mild overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FBecoming cloudy and mild
OL,13,Fwith some brighter spells, later
OL,14,Fspells of rain will spread eastwards
OL,15,Facross the region by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
