OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy and mild with occasional rain
OL,7,Fon Thursday, mainly in the west with
OL,8,Fstrengthening winds. Overnight rain
OL,9,Fclearing early Friday, then cooler
OL,10,Fwith blustery showers. Saturday turns
OL,11,Fdrier and settled.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
